data.name: ReadInterstateRequest
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, OTHER_STATE_CAS_ID, OTHR_STATE_FIPS_CD, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, OTH_ST_CASE_STATUS, CASE_TYPE, KS_CASE_IND, OTH_STATE_CLS_RES, OTH_STATE_CLS_DTE from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST where IDENTIFIER = @identifier

data.name: ReadInterstateRequestHistory
data.value: select top(1) INT_GENERATED_ID, CREATED_TSTAMP, CREATED_BY, TRANSACTION_DIRECT, TRANSACTION_SERIAL, ACTION_CODE, FUNCTIONAL_TYPE_CO, TRANSACTION_DATE, ACTION_REASON_CODE, ACTION_RES_DTE, ATTACHMENT_INDICAT, NOTE from CKT_INT_RQST_HIST where (@intGeneratedId = INT_GENERATED_ID) and (CREATED_TSTAMP = @createdTstamp)

data.name: UpdateInterstateRequestHistory
data.value: update CKT_INT_RQST_HIST set ACTION_RES_DTE = @actionResDte where (INT_GENERATED_ID = @intGeneratedId) and (CREATED_TSTAMP = @createdTstamp)
